Standards
  - tabs are two spaces
  - function names and variables lookLikeThis
  - Class names LookLikeThis
  - Avoid inheritance however use aggregation and interfaces
  - tests go into test file and end with Test
  - acceptance tests go into test/features
  
setup
  - install node
  - install npm
  - npm -g coffee-script tower forever grunt

install dependencies
  - npm install

watch files
  - cake watch
  
to install dependencies
  - npm install <dep-name> --save
  
to test
  all tests
    - cake test